A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fenvironment%2Fanswers%2F&d=fW%2FbMTssWaiVGVkll%2FHuLVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=73be8542\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.apple.com/hk/environment/answers/</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為了模擬顧客使用，我們測量產品在模擬情況下運行時所消耗的能源。每款產品有特定的每日使用模式，模式是基於顧客的實際和模擬使用數據結合所得。我們假設產品使用年期以作評估用途，由第一手擁有者計起，macOS 和 tvOS 裝置假定為四年，而 iOS 和 watchOS 裝置則假定為三年。<span style=\"color: red;\">大多數 Apple 產品實際上更耐用，還會由第一手擁有者轉贈、轉賣他人或送回 Apple，以供其他人繼續使用。</span>要了解更多有關我們產品能源耗用，請參閱我們的《產品環保報告》。"},{"pid":"ca284feadbc8030dca7cd5a563874b8e0cf19907","tid":449276,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T07:26:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Apple 機真係易死....<br />\n我自己用3星S3<br />\n用左5年<br />\n係有少少LAG左同廢左兩舊電<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但係KEEP住個個月fresh rom基本上打出打入WHATSAPP冇問題</span><br />\n唔似IPHONE 3年即死機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afebefb286d49318e750a84c593bcae850e55dce","tid":449276,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T07:32:52.000Z","msg":"而家i7+ i8  粒電都chur 勁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec8989f7a2a6ddaf23e39066f4e318ed66d240f","tid":449276,"uid":64956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T07:47:18.000Z","msg":"用有得換電嘅機同custom rom就好耐用<br />\n<br />\n三星S4宜家仲用得順"},{"pid":"9e7ba13e03f8e9cbcde10b4ba9c82a765431c842","tid":449276,"uid":121522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T07:47:47.000Z","msg":"5S 仍然使用中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d2c3e876aa2aff0b18c2f39c260234